eduled-tasks.test.js\n  79→- [ ] Test end-to-end task lifecycle\n  80→- [ ] Test bot notification on task execution\n  81→- [ ] Create tests/integration/f014-file-watchers.test.js\n  82→- [ ] Test file change detection and notification\n  83→- [ ] Test persistence across simulated restart\n  84→\n  85→## Phase 8: Prizm Docs Update\n  86→\n  87→- [ ] Update .prizm-docs/runtime.prizm with F-014 interfaces\n  88→- [ ] Update .prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm with new services\n  89→- [ ] Update .prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm with new commands\n  90→\n  91→## Dependencies\n  92→\n  93→- [ ] Install croner package: npm install croner\n  94→"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_fc1b22860b7f4ad68e98b8a4","__timestamp":"2026-03-12T21:33:29.680Z","_requestId":"0897e02cbc65495fa1b66af82a5de7ab"}
